comment:
* Constants related to a {@link SearchIndexableData}.
     *
     * This is the raw data that is stored into an Index. This is related to
     * {@link android.preference.Preference} and its attributes like
     * {@link android.preference.Preference#getTitle()},
     * {@link android.preference.Preference#getSummary()}, etc.

variables.name: COLUMN_SUMMARY_ON
variables.comment: * Summary's raw data when the data is "ON".

variables.name: COLUMN_SUMMARY_OFF
variables.comment: * Summary's raw data when the data is "OFF".

variables.name: COLUMN_ENTRIES
variables.comment: * Entries associated with the raw data (when the data can have several values).

variables.name: COLUMN_SCREEN_TITLE
variables.comment: * Fragment or Activity title associated with the raw data.

variables.name: COLUMN_KEY
variables.comment: * Key associated with the raw data. The key needs to be unique.

variables.name: COLUMN_USER_ID
variables.comment: * UserId associated with the raw data.

variables.name: PAYLOAD_TYPE
variables.comment:
* Identifier for the Payload object type.
         *
         * @hide

variables.name: PAYLOAD
variables.comment:
* Generic payload for improving Search result expressiveness.
         *
         * @hide
